text: Cymbaeremaeidae is a family of oribatids in the order Oribatida. There are about 5 genera and at least 90 described species in Cymbaeremaeidae. ==Genera== * Bulleremaeus Hammer, 1966 * Cymbaeremaeus Berlese, 1896 * Glanderemaeus Balogh & Csiszár, 1963 * Scapheremaeus Berlese, 1910 * Seteremaeus Hammer, 1971 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * Category:Acariformes
title: Cymbaeremaeidae
